Usage: set_advanced_rail_options [-help] [-reset]
                                 [-voltus_rail_include_file_begin <string>]
                                 [-voltus_rail_include_file_end <string>]

-help                                    # Prints out the command usage
-reset                                   # reset all advanced options
                                         # (bool, optional)
-voltus_rail_include_file_begin <string>
                                         # Vstorm2 include file (string, optional)
-voltus_rail_include_file_end <string>   # Vstorm2 include file
                                         # (string, optional)